Data represents Dental Assistants only; does not include dental therapists as dental therapists are unregulated in Canada and their information is not available. In addition, the profession is not regulated in some provinces. The Canada total includes provincial data in which registration with a regulatory authority may not be a condition of practice. As a result, the number of providers may be under-counted.  2017 Dental Assistant count for Newfoundland and Labrador, 2018  Dental Assistant count for Quebec and 2019  Dental Assistant count for Nova Scotia were used an estimate of the 2020 count, as their 2020 Dental Assistant data was not available. Prince Edward Island, Yukon, Northwest Territories and Nunavut data is excluded, as data is not available, does not exist or is not reported due to data quality concerns.
